high_descs: Turn around, take a step, turn to your left and move toward a cabinet by left side of the stove
Pick up the small fruit close to the wall
Turn to left and again to your left, move and turn right of the fridge to face the sink
Put the fruit in the sink basin with a glass, run the water, and pick the fruit up
Turn around, move forward to face the fridge
Open the fridge and place the fruit on the empty tray.
anns.task_desc: Place the cleaned fruit/apple in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and then head left to the kitchen counter
Pick up an apple off of the kitchen counter
Turn around and then head right so you are facing the left sink
Drop the apple in the right sink, run the faucet for a few seconds and pick up the apple again
Turn around and then turn right to face the fridge
Open the fridge, set the apple inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: Rinse an apple and put it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn to your right then cross the room head to the left side of the stove counter
Pick up the kiwi on the table
Turn to your left then walk straight and face the sink on your right
Put the kiwi in the sink and rinse it
Turn to your left walk forward to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the kiwi inside
anns.task_desc: Put the  clean kiwi in the fridge
